<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/shrin-honap> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Shrinivas Honap is a Chartered accountant by profession and served with Vodafone, Capita, KPMG and Egg during his executive career. Shrin currently holds the following Non Executive roles; Non Executive and Chair of Audit at Financial Ombudsman’s Service, House Of Commons Commission, Corps Security, One Touch Switching Company. He also sits on the Civil service Pensions Board. He has previously served at Office of Legal Complaints, Office of the Public Guardian and Rural Payments Agency, UJ Atomic Energy Authority , CMA and the NHS. Shrin is the Chair of the Audit Committee for NWS and has particular interests in large transformation programmes, Risk Management, Finance and Developing Technology."@en .
